commit 942a9d876a1c7526845700a9824b4204d8dbf0c8
Author: Charles Dang <exodia339@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Feb 12 10:49:29 2018 +1100

    Removed /red, /yellow, and /green chat commands
    
    These are admin-only, used old GUI1 formatting, and while it would have been rather
    simple to get them working in the GUI2 chatbox (I think), it's not really worth it.
    These commands just aren't very useful.

